package main

import (
	"bytes"
	"encoding/base64"
	"encoding/hex"
	"fmt"
	"image/png"
	"time"
)

func main() {

	for _, f := range frames() {
		dec, err := hex.DecodeString(f)
		if err != nil {
			panic(err)
		}

		m, err := png.Decode(bytes.NewReader(dec))
		if err != nil {
			panic(err)
		}

		var buf bytes.Buffer
		err = png.Encode(&buf, m)
		if err != nil {
			panic(err)
		}

		imgStr := "IMAGE:" + base64.StdEncoding.EncodeToString(buf.Bytes())
		fmt.Print("\x0c", imgStr)
		time.Sleep(100 * time.Millisecond)
	}
}
